metadata.name: wading blue
metadata.description:
December 10ᵗʰ 2022

There have been many things that have gone through since the beginning of 2022.  
Turbulence makes it very draining of thoughts, time, energy, and emotions.  
Hoping for dreams and hopes to come true.  
Swallowing every bitter pill that comes your way (enjoying it even though it ends up complaining anyway).

Hey, you! Hopefully, tomorrow can be someone stronger and braver than anything.  
There is still a lot to go through, learn, and understand.
